        "content": "<div>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #ccc; padding: 8px 0;\">\n    KPI North Star: Indice di Conversione e Copertura Ecosistema\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; padding: 10px; flex-wrap: nowrap;\">\n\n    <div style=\"text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0;\">\n      <div\n        style=\"border: 1px solid #5794F2; border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 12px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; height: 17px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-sizing: content-box;\">\n        [1. SEND]</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #8e8e8e; margin-top: 4px; white-space: nowrap;\">(Invia MDC)</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"flex-grow: 1; height: 31px; display: flex; align-items: center; margin: 0 8px;\">\n      <div style=\"flex-grow: 1; height: 1px; background-color: #ccc;\"></div>\n      <div\n        style=\"width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 4px solid transparent; border-bottom: 4px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #ccc;\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0;\">\n      <div\n        style=\"border: 1px solid #5794F2; border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 12px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; height: 17px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-sizing: content-box;\">\n        [2. EMD]</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #8e8e8e; margin-top: 4px; white-space: nowrap;\">(Accetta/Scarta)</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"flex-grow: 1; height: 31px; display: flex; align-items: center; margin: 0 8px;\">\n      <div style=\"flex-grow: 1; height: 1px; background-color: #ccc;\"></div>\n      <div\n        style=\"width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 4px solid transparent; border-bottom: 4px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #ccc;\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0;\">\n      <div\n        style=\"border: 1px solid #5794F2; border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 12px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; height: 17px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-sizing: content-box;\">\n        [3. PSP]</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #8e8e8e; margin-top: 4px; white-space: nowrap;\">(Smistamento)</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"flex-grow: 1; height: 31px; display: flex; align-items: center; margin: 0 8px;\">\n      <div style=\"flex-grow: 1; height: 1px; background-color: #ccc;\"></div>\n      <div\n        style=\"width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 4px solid transparent; border-bottom: 4px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #ccc;\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0;\">\n      <div\n        style=\"border: 1px solid #5794F2; border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 12px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; height: 17px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-sizing: content-box;\">\n        [4. PORTALE SEND]</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #8e8e8e; margin-top: 4px; white-space: nowrap;\">(Visualizzazione)</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"flex-grow: 1; height: 31px; display: flex; align-items: center; margin: 0 8px;\">\n      <div style=\"flex-grow: 1; height: 1px; background-color: #ccc;\"></div>\n      <div\n        style=\"width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 4px solid transparent; border-bottom: 4px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #ccc;\">\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0;\">\n      <div\n        style=\"border: 1px solid #5794F2; border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 12px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; height: 17px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-sizing: content-box;\">\n        [5. APP BANCARIA]</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #8e8e8e; margin-top: 4px; white-space: nowrap;\">(Pagamento)</div>\n    </div>\