          "query": "MessageVolumeSnapshot\r\n| where window_start >= startofday(ago(1d)) and window_start < startofday(now())\r\n| summarize TotaleEventi = coalesce(sum(message_sent_count), 0) + coalesce(sum(message_discarded_count), 0)\r\n| extend ['Stato Servizio'] = iff(TotaleEventi > 0, \"OPERATIVO\", \"NON OPERATIVO\")\r\n| project ['Stato Servizio']",
